From: Frank Hermann <frank@hermann-essen.de>
Date: Sun, 11 Jan 2026 23:48:02 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] fix(mcp-server): normalize tool definitions without violating
 exactOptionalPropertyTypes

- accept tool definitions with optional description from getToolDefinitions()
- omit description property when undefined instead of forcing empty strings
- keep ToolDefinition output strict and upstream-compatible
- avoid any-casts and preserve semantic meaning of optional fields
